THE CRYSTAL STRUCTURE WAS OBTAINED BY INCUBATING TRYPSIN 
WITH THE T-BUTOXY-ALA-VAL-BOROLYS-C10H16 PARA-TOLUENESULFONIC 
ACID IN THE PRESENCE OF ETHANOL.
